            "text": "That tan and orange two-tone exterior sure is a head-turner, perfectly accentuating what’s already an attractive body. As is the case with any build, the devil is in the details and someone really paid attention to them on this car. For example, the side mirror caps are painted tan to match the upper portion of the body. Pinstriping separates the two body colors, growing thicker as it progresses to the rear. Mirror-like chrome on the bumpers and other trim pieces add some nice highlights. You’ll also note the SS-style hood with venting and 17-inch torque thrust alloy wheels for a more performance-tilted feel. Even the tinted windows add to the customized, unique presentation.",
